{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":256686,"duration_api_ms":246345,"num_turns":10,"result":"Here's a summary of the two bugs and the fix:\n\n### Bug 1: Uncaught exceptions leave entities stuck (primary cause)\n`processStage()` line 167 had no try-catch around `serviceFunction.apply(dto)`. If `PolicyService.evaluate()` threw any RuntimeException (NPE, DB connection error, etc.), the exception bypassed all retry/failure handling, and the entity stayed at LABELED with `processingCode=0` permanently. Recovery would pick it up every 80s but hit the same exception repeatedly.\n\n**Fix:** Wrapped the service call in try-catch. Exceptions are now retried up to 3 times with backoff, then recorded as a failure with `code=-1` so the entity exits the state machine cleanly.\n\n### Bug 2: Stage advanced unconditionally, even on failure\nLines 208-210 always set `processingStage=nextStage` regardless of success/failure. A LABELED entity that failed during policy evaluation would be written to DB as stage=EVALUATED with a non-zero code — masking where the actual failure occurred.\n\n**Fix:** Stage is now only advanced when `serviceSuccess=true`. On failure, the entity stays at its current stage (LABELED) with the error code, making it clear where processing actually failed.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"55462ef7-81d3-474e-bf6a-7a929889d26b","total_cost_usd":0.91098545,"usage":{"input_tokens":9,"cache_creation_input_tokens":40437,"cache_read_input_tokens":239381,"output_tokens":6803,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":40437,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6[1m]":{"inputTokens":9,"outputTokens":6803,"cacheReadInputTokens":239381,"cacheCreationInputTokens":40437,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.54254175,"contextWindow":1000000,"maxOutputTokens":64000},"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":66,"outputTokens":7395,"cacheReadInputTokens":2270452,"cacheCreationInputTokens":83486,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.36844370000000004,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"terminal_reason":"completed","fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"416e1310-7245-4030-a0c2-24b15b01f5f1"}
